Portions of this package's test data and source are derived from MoSQITo
(https://github.com/Eomys/MoSQITo), licensed under the Apache License 2.0
(see LICENSE-MoSQITo in this directory):

- test/data/din45692_band_levels.jl: 28-band levels computed from the
  DIN 45692:2009 chapter-6 test signals vendored by MoSQITo; reference
  sharpness values transcribed from
  validations/sq_metrics/sharpness_din/validation_sharpness_din.py.
- test/data/mosqito_crosscheck.jl: expected values computed by running
  MoSQITo's sharpness_din_from_loudness.
- src/weighting_fastl.jl: weighting table transcribed from
  mosqito/sq_metrics/sharpness/sharpness_din/_weighting_fastl.py.
- test/data/dw_fig3_references.jl: Zwicker & Fastl roughness reference
  values from validations/sq_metrics/roughness_dw/input/references.py
  (MoSQITo commit d990c33f94f1).
- test/data/mosqito_roughness_crosscheck.jl: expected values computed by
  running MoSQITo's roughness_dw.
- src/bark.jl, src/roughness_dw_tables.jl: conversion and weighting tables
  transcribed from mosqito/utils and
  mosqito/sq_metrics/roughness/roughness_dw (MoSQITo commit d990c33f94f1).
- test/support/am_generator.jl: transcribed from mosqito/utils/am_sine_generator.py.
- src/roughness_dw.jl: transcribed from mosqito/sq_metrics/roughness/roughness_dw/_roughness_dw_main_calc.py, sound_level_meter/comp_spectrum.py and utils/time_segmentation.py (MoSQITo commit d990c33f94f1).
